Women's Organizations in Stevens County

  • Women's Organizations in Stevens County
  • Olivia.carlson.98@gmail.com
  • carl5004
  • jekyllrb

This website is the home for a digital exhibit on women's organizations in Stevens County, Minnesota. It includes the Pomme de Terre Gardening Club, Framnas Jolly Workers, and League of Women Voters Stevens County. This exhibit has a focus on digital humanities and what it means to be a feminist.
